data.description: The outside of the house is much nicer during the summer and spring the arch of the sidewalk is filled with roses there’s flowers all around the house the trees bloom beautifully. Small town living located 20 miles Northeast from Emporia. 50 miles south of Topeka. Newly remodeled 3 bedroom, 1 bath with home office. Or 4 bedrooms Located on a large corner lot. New roof, siding, central heat and air, windows, insulation and PEX Plumbing. New paint, trim and hardwood floors. High ceiling in the living room. Homemade wood trim in the dining room.Built-in closet and desk in bedroom. Master bedroom is 220 square feet. Privacy fence surrounds large back yard. Patio doors that lead you right out on the 35*11 foot deck. Includes washer dryer hookup, off street parking and two sheds. Appliances are included. Don't wait this like brand new home is  reduced to 39000 with yearly taxes under $600.  I didn't put pics of the bedrooms,  cause I don't want all stuff online,  call and set up a appointment to show..
